invalid_files = []
p = subprocess.Popen([sys.executable, self._coverage_file,
    '--pydev-analyze'], stdout=subprocess.PIPE, stdin=subprocess.PIPE,
    stderr=subprocess.PIPE)
__, stderrdata = p.communicate('|'.join(files).encode())
if stderrdata:
    match = re.search('Invalid files not passed to coverage: (.*?)$',
        stderrdata.decode(), re.M)
    if match:
        invalid_files = [f.strip() for f in match.group(1).split(',')]
return invalid_files
